== Spec Goodies Plugin

A collection of utilities for use in writing RSpec specifications.

=== More Information

For more information, be sure to look through the documentation over at RubyForge:

* http://faithfulcode.rubyforge.org/docs/spec_goodies

You might also enjoy taking a look at the specs for the plugin:

* http://faithfulcode.rubyforge.org/svn/plugins/trunk/spec_goodies/spec

Browse the complete source code:

* http://faithfulcode.rubyforge.org/svn/plugins/trunk/spec_goodies

